data.description: Available for showings FEB 1. Whether it's your starter home or forever home, this energy efficient lovely 3/2 is located in desirable western Palm Beach County. Stay safe in storm with new, clean hurricane proof windows and air conditioning! With spacious room inside and a large mango tree outside you wont want to leave the country style home in the best area!  Just minutes from shopping, parks, restaurants, and the brand new Dr. Garcia High school this is the perfect family home! The closest major intersection is Lake Worth and Lyons Roads. With room for the dogs, and a fully fenced backyard shaded by a large olive tree, this gem offers privacy WITHOUT an HOA, and a 20 minute drive to the ocean. A must see, lowest price in it's neighborhood. It will not last long!
